Simultaneously, on the home front, Cozmo was releasing a new version of their home fitness bike. 
The home fitness bike was also equipped with a lot of sensors and gadgets. It came with a mobile gaming app. 
Home fitness bikers could connect their bike to the TV or a tablet and get interactive bike lessons from Cozmo's fitness channel. 
They could also buy Cozmo's Virtual Reality goggles and experience a 3D bike ride through various scenic routes along with their buddies. 
It was Cozmo's foray into the metaverse.